\end{align*}

{/eq}

The antiderivative of the given function is:

{eq}\mathbf{\frac{4}{x} + \frac{5}{2}\ln |x| + \frac{9}{4}\ln |x+2| + \frac{9}{4}\ln |x-2| + C}

